txt.en: 'Retreat! Back to the battlements of Gramsfoot!'
'Drive these curs out of my base, you lazy sluggards. You fight like goblins! They're beatin' me!'
'Come face me within the keep you worthless slugs! I'll not venture into a trap.'
'Hold this line Ongbûrz scum! They must not drive me from this keep!'
'To arms you pissant worms, I spy a force!'
